  "title": "Hotel Front Office Officer | 5 star Hotel",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Front Office Executive</strong></u><br /><br /><strong>Salary: $2,200 - $2,500 (negotiable)</strong><br /><strong>5 days work week, 44 hours (including weekends and PH)</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Rotating shift</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assist guests with check-in, check-out, and cashiering duties.</li><li>Welcome guests, complete registration, and issue room keys. </li><li>Assist with guest requests, feedback, and provide accurate information.</li><li>Manage guest messages, mail, and phone calls courteously. </li><li>Increase room revenue through up-selling and securing the best rates for walk-in guests.</li><li>Support and guide Guest Relations Assistants and ensure smooth Front Office operations.</li><li>Maintain Front Desk cleanliness and follow hotel policies, safety, and payment procedures.</li><li>Perform any related duties or special projects assigned by the Front Office leadership team.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Min. 2 years of hotel Front Office experience</li><li>Able to read, write and speak English fluently to communicate with guest.</li><li>Friendly and engaging service attitude.</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Can do rotating shift</li></ul><p><u><strong>Additional Benefits</strong></u></p><ul><li>AWS</li><li>Variable Bonus</li><li>Meals provided</li><li>Medical benefits </li><li>Birthday Leave </li><li>Annual leaves</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Hey Rocket Pte. Ltd. (EA 21C0816)</strong><br /><strong>Pui Hui Lee (R25127133)</strong></p>",
